    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000006",
    "sentence": "及沛公略地過陽武，蒼以客從攻南陽。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "沛",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 1,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000007",
    "sentence": "蒼當斬，解衣伏質，身長大，肥白如瓠，時王陵見而怪其美士，乃言沛公，赦勿斬。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "沛",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 30,
        "end": 31
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000008",
    "sentence": "遂西入武關，至咸陽。",
    "entities": [
