        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000010",
    "sentence": "陳餘擊走常山王張耳，耳歸漢。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000011",
    "sentence": "漢以蒼為常山守。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000012",
    "sentence": "從韓信擊趙，蒼得陳餘。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000013",
    "sentence": "趙地已平，漢王以蒼為代相，備邊冠。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000014",
    "sentence": "已而徙為趙相，相趙王耳。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000015",
    "sentence": "耳卒，相其子敖。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000016",
    "sentence": "復徙相代。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_042_000017",
    "sentence": "燕王臧荼反，蒼以代相從攻荼有功，封為北平侯，食邑千二百戶。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "食邑",
